HEADWORD: Valvule
<hw>Valv"ule</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>valvule</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A little valve; a valvelet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small valvelike
